      "timestampEdited": null,
      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "Some people have access to a mostly compatible Cadence PDK through agreements with other entities and have successfully taped out.\n\nAs well, GF will *not* respond to requests for the PDK without other relationships with them already.",
